text: Hi, if I need to get data from an API to use on a site hosted on HubSpot, what languages are  supported by HubSpot?  If there's a link with this information please add it, I didn't found nothing related... Thanks
As far as I'm aware you're pretty much limited to JS, unless you want to build some kind of integration to populate a HubDB with external data regularly
<@U88BQKDCK> You can make an AJAX call using jQuery in a script on your page: <http://api.jquery.com/jquery.ajax/>
thanks, I will try the jQuery and JS option thanks <@U26BLKGE4> <@U6GNQ7JBU>!
